Series.Overview: In 30 lives, Marina Orsini plays the role of Gabrielle, a professor in a multiethnic high school. 30 lives, is also the story of 29 students from Gabrielle, which we will follow the stories and plots throughout the season. But 30 lives is, first and foremost, the story of lives that come together, collide, and who, day after day, will vibrate Quebec.
